name: Felidae
description:
if i could talk :
I know you are not a threat, that's why I know I always want to come to you..

but what a surprise if you douse, throw, even kill me with poison, what did I do wrong to make you like that

I don't need to be given good food, just the food you used to eat is enough, we are stray cats but we don't plan to exploit you until you are poor, let alone kill you..
